_sText:
This is my tablesoccer game project (beta) made on 3-4 days, its a 2v2, created for jail maps but just a mg for now i hope u like it enjoy! :)

Steering:

W = up   
A = spin left

S = down       
D = Spin right

Leftclick = Shoot

Rightclick = shift between players

Thx to Waffle and Tohru anyway but mostly made by my self :)

Thanks for downloading!, and comment if u find some bugs :D
